  "The power rule states d/dx(x^n) = nx^(n-1). It works for any real exponent n, including fractions and negatives.": "电源规则表示 d/dx( xn) = nx(n-1) 。 它适用于任何真正的前列n , 包括分数和负数 。",
  "What does the constant multiple rule state?": "常数多重规则状态是什么?",
  "d/dx[c*f(x)] = c*f'(x), where c is a constant": "ddx[c*f(x)] = c*f'(x), c为常数",
  "d/dx[c*f(x)] = c*f(x) + f'(x)": "ddx[c*f(x)] = c*f(x) + f'(x)",
