  "d/dx[f(x) - g(x)] = f(x) - g(x)": "ddx[f(x) - g(x)] = f(x) - g(x)",
  "The difference rule states the derivative of a difference equals the difference of the derivatives: d/dx[f - g] = f' - g'.": "差价规则规定,差价的衍生物等于衍生物的区别:d/dx[f-g]=f'-g'。",
  "What does it mean to 'rewrite before differentiating'?": "区别前重写是什么意思?",
  "Converting expressions like 1/x^2 to x^(-2) or sqrt(x) to x^(1/2) so the power rule can be applied directly": "将表达式转换为 1/ x% 2 到 x% (-2) 或 sqrt( x) 到 x% ( 1/2) , 权力规则可以直接应用",
