  "Finding the second derivative before the first": "在第一个衍生物之前查找第二个衍生物",
  "Rewriting expressions in the form x^n (e.g., 1/x = x^(-1), sqrt(x) = x^(1/2)) allows direct application of the power rule.": "以表xn (例如, 1/x = x(-1), sqrt(x) = x( 1/2)) 格式重写表达式, 允许直接应用权力规则 。",
